Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.86,0:00:14.86,OP2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}The low sky looks like it's about to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.36,0:00:20.33,OP2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,150)}I spit a mixture of saliva and agitation on the sidewalk.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.25,0:00:24.79,OP2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,50)\org(0,0)}I cower at the thought of tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.67,0:00:27.96,OP2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,0)\org(0,0)}Worrying that everything might fall apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.96,0:00:30.42,OP2,,0000,0000,0000,,In my heart, I know that looking ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.42,0:00:33.93,OP2,,0000,0000,0000,,To the day after tomorrow won't give me a single answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.93,0:00:39.76,OP2,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow is like an empty canvas that extends endlessly;
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.76,0:00:42.77,OP2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,150)}What should I sketch on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.69,0:00:53.78,OP2,,0000,0000,0000,,Reality begins to stain the canvas black;
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.78,0:00:56.45,OP2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,150)}What should I draw?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.70,0:01:00.33,OP2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,150)}I struggle to shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.14,0:01:28.15,OP2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)\org(0,0)}Tomorrow is like an empty canvas that extends endlessly;
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.15,0:01:31.02,OP2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,150)\org(0,0)}What should I sketch on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:41.91,OP2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,0)\org(0,0)}Reality begins to stain the canvas black;
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.91,0:01:44.87,OP2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,150)\org(0,0)}What should I draw?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.75,0:01:48.67,OP2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,200)\org(0,0)}I struggle to shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.79,0:22:43.63,ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\org(0,0)\blur3}"Do dreams exist at a time like this?"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.50,0:22:47.34,ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\org(0,0)\blur3}I've gotten tired of speaking like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.55,0:22:51.47,ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\org(0,0)\blur3}I've been walking this entire time,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.43,0:22:54.76,ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\org(0,0)\blur3}but recently, even that seems fruitless and in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.51,0:22:57.10,ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\org(0,0)\blur3}{\an7}"I want to see you."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.43,0:22:58.64,ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\org(0,0)\blur3}{\an9}An irrelevant phrase
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.39,0:23:03.02,ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\org(0,0)\blur3}often heard sung round and round the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.73,0:23:04.86,ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\org(0,0)\blur3}{\an7}Something like that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.15,0:23:08.11,ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\org(0,0)\blur3\pos(2520,37.5)}{\an9}No, something like that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.57,0:23:07.03,ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\org(0,0)\blur3}{\an7}isn't enough to satisfy me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.73,0:23:10.82,ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\org(0,0)\blur3\an7}I know exactly how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.66,0:23:17.20,ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\org(0,0)\blur3\}{\an9}We're free. We pray that all dreams eventually come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.12,0:23:19.16,ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\org(0,0)\blur3}{\an7}Just like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.54,0:23:20.62,ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\org(0,0)\blur3}everyone searches for their true selves.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.50,0:23:25.00,ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\org(0,0)\blur3}What we find after a long journey
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.71,0:23:26.75,ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\org(0,0)\blur3}{\an9}is the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.46,0:23:30.63,ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\org(0,0)\blur3}We're free. We seek the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.34,0:23:34.60,ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\org(0,0)\blur3}We float freely like butterflies.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.30,0:23:36.51,ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\org(0,0)\blur3}Our hearts reflect the great blue sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.22,0:23:40.69,ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\org(0,0)\blur3}Even if we happen to lose our freedom amidst a strong wind,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.64,0:23:43.65,ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\org(0,0)\blur3}we never want to feel regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.11,0:23:50.19,ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\org(0,0)\blur3}We're free. We seek the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.07,0:23:54.07,ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\org(0,0)\blur3}We're free. We long to reach a new height.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.49,0:01:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.33,0:01:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The past will follow you, wherever you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.37,0:01:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.92,0:01:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Slasher attacked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.46,0:01:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, yeah. {\i1}Banzai!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.63,0:01:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.59,0:01:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you want to join the Dollars...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.55,0:01:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.55,0:01:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't run from your past.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.84,0:01:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.67,0:01:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A great man once said that the world is a myth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.51,0:01:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think he said it, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.97,0:01:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he didn't,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.01,0:02:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure someone else said something similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.18,0:02:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.14,0:02:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How ya been?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.52,0:02:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.93,0:02:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cheap!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.23,0:02:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I give you discount, President Kadota.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.77,0:02:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's a president?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.94,0:02:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five of your cheapest nigiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.48,0:02:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.32,0:02:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what do you want, head of the Yellow Scarves?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.91,0:02:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To us, the realm of fiction is as important as reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.95,0:02:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The two are equal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.42,0:02:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's not that we dislike reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.59,0:02:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd understand if I said that the head of the Yellow Scarves wanted to talk to the Dollars?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.43,0:02:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just so we're clear, we don't know many details,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.85,0:02:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the Slasher's taken out some of us, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.56,0:02:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, we'd be happy if you could clear up this misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.98,0:02:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.78,0:02:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drink tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.98,0:02:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catechin's good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.57,0:03:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.53,0:03:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, President Kadota.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.78,0:03:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still your heart, and even flame will feel cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.54,0:03:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.87,0:03:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't really know what that means, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.42,0:03:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm amazed you can hold a teacup that hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.34,0:03:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys may be the only ones thinking that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.64,0:03:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Dollars have no vertical or horizontal connections.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.64,0:03:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So there could be a group of them doing the slashings, and you just don't know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.69,0:03:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if they attack other members of their gang, they won't be suspected.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Makes sense, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.16,0:03:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.99,0:03:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would a group, uninterested in money and fame,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.12,0:03:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,try to use the Slasher attacks to destroy the Yellow Scarves?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.21,0:03:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I knew. It might be a personal vendetta.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A personal vendetta?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never heard of the Dollars fighting with the Yellow Scarves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.47,0:04:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not the Dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.85,0:04:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue Square.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.43,0:04:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kida...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.44,0:04:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forget what they did to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.56,0:04:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After what happened, things calmed for the moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.23,0:04:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but that doesn't mean people have forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.32,0:04:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.19,0:04:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you came to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.57,0:04:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You would know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.78,0:04:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me who the leader of the Dollars is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.41,0:04:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you can, how many of your old Blue Square friends are-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.21,0:04:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man. Kida...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.96,0:04:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't mistake reality for your delusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.34,0:04:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue Square never existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.76,0:04:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that for the best?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saki... Saki was attacked by people who don't exist, and she's still in the hospital-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:05:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.44,0:05:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your ex was done in by a group that doesn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.94,0:05:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.28,0:05:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Karisawa, I'm going to lose my temper!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.99,0:05:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've already lost it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.03,0:05:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Yumacchi lost his first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.91,0:05:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're even.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like you're mad over what happened to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.67,0:05:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,some people are mad over what  you're saying about the Dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.84,0:05:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Given that, if you can't call it even, then you shouldn't come talk to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.31,0:05:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that we're blameless in the matter,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.27,0:05:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if you're going to bring up the past, when it was
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dotachin who saved her and you who ran away...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.19,0:05:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll just treat the whole thing like a delusion that never happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If reality and fiction are equal, then any reality you don't need can just be called delusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.20,0:05:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how we do things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong, Karisawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.04,0:05:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:06:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if there was a Blue Square,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.21,0:06:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue Square were the first ones to get the crap kicked out of them in that episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.09,0:06:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But for some reason, they're getting treated like the only bad guys here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.72,0:06:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm complaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.97,0:06:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.01,0:06:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.27,0:06:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.69,0:06:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.86,0:06:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.98,0:06:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the ones who should apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.11,0:06:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We do feel bad about what happened with Saki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.95,0:06:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I should be thanking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.45,0:06:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got every right to hate us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.12,0:06:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did all that to a middle school kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.46,0:06:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Kadota, you didn't do anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much you try to escape it, you can't get away from what you were part of.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.22,0:06:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But let me make this perfectly clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.51,0:06:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who the boss is, and I ain't looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.56,0:06:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And one more time, the Dollars have nothing to do with the Slasher
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.94,0:07:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and no reason to pick a fight with the Yellow Scarves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.44,0:07:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.15,0:07:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was one person, though, who said they knew who the boss is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.07,0:07:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.32,0:07:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you gonna do when you find out?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you get the boss's name from him,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.12,0:07:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are you gonna go have a nice cup of tea with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.41,0:07:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or are you gonna get the Yellow Scarves together and kidnap him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.54,0:07:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to find the Slasher.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.30,0:07:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do the rest of the Yellow Scarves agree with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.67,0:07:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you had a firm hand on them like you did, I could trust and help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.43,0:07:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But while you were gone, they changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you haven't noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.65,0:07:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still think they're my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know what you should do, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.24,0:07:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it was the Dollars,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.91,0:08:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,doesn't it have nothing to do with you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You hated fights between groups. That's why you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.08,0:08:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.71,0:08:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But sometimes, the reality you thought you'd gotten rid of, returns in a warped way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this time, it's not just my friends in the Yellow Scarves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.97,0:08:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone very important to me, someone with nothing to do with my past or the Yellow Scarves, was attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.64,0:08:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I can't forgive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.43,0:08:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's your...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.94,0:08:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's my problem and mine alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.15,0:08:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just using them... Using the Yellow Scarves as an excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you know that much, then I won't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.83,0:08:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let that guy who knows the boss and the boss himself decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.25,0:08:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.25,0:08:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you guys do decide that we're your enemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.17,0:08:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we do... Then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.97,0:08:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want a fight, you'll get one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.97,0:08:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're ready for that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.18,0:09:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you realize that, if you're doing this for revenge,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's on a totally different level than the kiddy fights that kids your age have.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.07,0:09:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're scaring the other customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.08,0:09:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're gonna talk like that, do it outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.46,0:09:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five Kremlin nigiri, Mr. President!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.17,0:09:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fight 'cause you're hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat and be full!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Full of dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.17,0:09:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A man's stomach is a factory of dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.43,0:09:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Simon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.10,0:09:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... L-Let's eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.81,0:09:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That chef's too dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.73,0:09:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, isn't this usually attempted murder?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know you could stab a knife that deeply.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.33,0:10:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you, Kida.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.74,0:10:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do anything you'll regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that chef's one scary mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.63,0:10:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A few inches either way, and there'd have been a body.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I thought he was cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.84,0:10:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.09,0:10:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw him in my mind, fighting sambo style
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.55,0:10:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with the hero of a cooking manga who says not to play with knives!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, in our minds, the chef became
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.52,0:10:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a former Russian Armed Forces martial arts instructor, who once fought the mafia!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.90,0:10:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He might just be pretending to be a sushi chef as a cover!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.61,0:10:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wouldn't open a restaurant as conspicuous as Russian Sushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.24,0:10:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Horoda... Horoda...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, Kadota? Is that some new spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.58,0:10:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dotachin chanted {\i1}Ho Rodaho Roda{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think it's a root spell or a summon spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.75,0:10:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Might be lightning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.79,0:10:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember what Kida was saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.88,0:10:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already told you this,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:10:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you can investigate the Dollars all you want, and you won't find the Slasher.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.26,0:11:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... No, we disagree.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.51,0:11:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.47,0:11:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a rumor that the black biker is part of the Dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.35,0:11:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are we talking about the black biker all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.35,0:11:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last night, we saw something unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.11,0:11:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the Black Rider helped someone with a katana escape,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.61,0:11:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which means they're working with the Slasher.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.36,0:11:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.66,0:11:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A guy named Horoda said he was attacked by the black biker once before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.66,0:11:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Horoda?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Horoda...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so that's why you were muttering "Horoda".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.75,0:11:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big deal about Horoda?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.25,0:11:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing big...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.17,0:11:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But yeah, I may be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.84,0:11:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong about what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.22,0:11:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just, I think I once knew a guy with that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.10,0:11:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's a group, within the Dollars, working with the Black Rider,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.40,0:11:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they're attacking the Yellow Scarves, things would make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.69,0:12:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yumacchi, that doesn't make any sense, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.36,0:12:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.16,0:12:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The black biker took out the Slasher once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.78,0:12:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Togusa rammed the guy with a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.79,0:12:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then Shizu smashed him with a door.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.66,0:12:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there were fifty other attacks that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.96,0:12:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But those guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.84,0:12:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, there'll be no more Slasher.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.22,0:12:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They picked a fight with Heiwajima Shizuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.64,0:12:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can guess what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.01,0:12:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the phone number of the guy who knows the boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.81,0:12:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do what you want with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.07,0:12:43.61,Default-no margin,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheer up, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.11,0:12:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gloomy faces scare away customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.28,0:12:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat that and leave the place smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.58,0:12:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.20,0:12:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're happy enough. Don't take others' happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.67,0:13:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Share it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.88,0:13:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I just learned this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.97,0:13:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The merciless are failed catfish."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.34,0:13:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Mercy benefits yourself, as well as others," you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.43,0:13:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a catfish, Mr. Kida?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.31,0:13:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey. Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.06,0:13:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.52,0:13:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.36,0:13:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having nothing to do is really boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.86,0:13:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I punch you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.36,0:13:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shut up. I'm paying you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.28,0:13:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this chocolate you sent to the Awakusu-Kai?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.83,0:13:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a handgun. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Six months ago, someone ran away with some handguns from the Awakusu-Kai, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.13,0:13:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.88,0:13:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one that horrible Dullahan was after, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.09,0:13:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.97,0:13:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Celty got most of them before they could cause a problem,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.39,0:13:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but there's still one out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.93,0:13:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.98,0:14:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd be calling soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bluff?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.44,0:14:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.11,0:14:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be there soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.86,0:14:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, you yourself were the only one who couldn't run from the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.95,0:14:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A great man once said that the world is symbolic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.25,0:14:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think he said it, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.83,0:14:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he didn't, I'm sure someone else said something similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen you make that face in a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.30,0:14:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same one you used to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.92,0:14:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were a middle schooler, but it was an adult's face.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While I enjoy my remembrance of things past, let me welcome you like so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.18,0:14:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.56,0:14:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I know what you're here to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.02,0:14:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could've told you on the phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.40,0:14:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's a bit too serious for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.49,0:14:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard your friend got slashed?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.37,0:14:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sonohara Anri, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.99,0:15:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like she's more important to you than the kids in the Yellow Scarves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once upon a time, a young boy, influenced by manga and TV shows,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.80,0:15:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,made a group called the "Yellow Scarves."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Yellow Scarves fought another group, with a Blue Flag,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and were in great peril.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.93,0:15:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then a brilliant strategist appeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.31,0:15:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are they all girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.56,0:15:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it wasn't Shokatsu Koumei.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.23,0:15:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was more like Sousou?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.52,0:15:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then the other group, now in peril itself, kidnapped the young boy's princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The boy tried to save her but got scared halfway...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.03,0:15:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the girl you like was caught up in a Yellow Scarves gang war and badly hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.91,0:15:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, I see... This is just like what happened with Saki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.59,0:15:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you're thinking this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.46,0:15:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I thought I loved Saki,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.13,0:15:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I was too scared to save her."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.10,0:15:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it wasn't true love.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.43,0:16:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you were just after her body.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.14,0:16:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you didn't love her as much as you thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.11,0:16:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good lord, he goes on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.57,0:16:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And as time passed, you actually wanted that to be the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.65,0:16:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which would mean that if you really loved a girl, you could risk your life to protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.20,0:16:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now Sonohara Anri's your chance to find out, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.71,0:16:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you believe that, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to do it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.55,0:16:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get your revenge on the Slasher?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.67,0:16:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or destroy the Dollars?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.47,0:16:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Depending on your answer, it might be both.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.47,0:16:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like that resolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.43,0:16:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.97,0:16:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is to keep you going forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.19,0:16:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll tell you the facts, the truth, and the unvarnished reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.48,0:16:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The three are normally different, but they're sometimes the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.41,0:16:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, how's Mikado doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You introduced me to him this spring,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.50,0:17:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your friend, Ryuugamine Mikado.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.96,0:17:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you mentioning him now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.92,0:17:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking he must be really worried about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.55,0:17:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got nothing to do with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.76,0:17:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't told him about the Yellow Scarves.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.31,0:17:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the same as always - quiet, but doing really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.64,0:17:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He seems like he's enjoying every day of his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.77,0:17:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you jealous of his peaceful life?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.48,0:17:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This has nothing to do with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.61,0:17:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if it did?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.61,0:17:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, I see... Mikado's doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.66,0:17:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His friend's suffering so much, and he, the cause of this suffering, is enjoying his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.38,0:17:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, Izaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.09,0:17:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.96,0:17:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The head of the Dollars is your beloved best friend, Ryuugamine Mikado.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.01,0:18:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, you may be the only one of you two who thinks you're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.85,0:18:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reality is always a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.22,0:18:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fed up with it, we decided to remake the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.44,0:18:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make walls, divide things into trash and things we care about,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.32,0:18:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,leave what we loved inside and kick the rest outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.36,0:18:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when we tried it, it really worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.32,0:18:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can make a world out of nothing but {\i1}moe {\i0}and {\i1}tsundere {\i0}and {\i1}BL{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.62,0:18:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was an amazing discovery!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.70,0:18:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the one good way to distinguish between reality and fiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.29,0:18:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Kanra> Did you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.71,0:18:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Dollars and Yellow Scarves went at it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.55,0:18:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Tanaka Tarou> Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.55,0:18:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Setton> Scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.72,0:18:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Tanaka Tarou> But it's just another small-scale fight, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.84,0:18:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Kanra> Actually, this time, they attacked the Yellow Scarves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.89,0:18:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Setton> Wow, bold!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.18,0:18:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Kanra> That Headless Rider, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.47,0:18:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say it teamed up with the Slasher and attacked their secret base! LOL
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.36,0:18:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Setton> Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.27,0:18:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Kanra> What's wrong, Setton?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.07,0:18:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Tanaka Tarou> No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.40,0:18:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't believe that, even from you, Kanra.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.82,0:19:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's preposterous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.53,0:19:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}<Saika has joined the channel>
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.37,0:19:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Saika> What are you all talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.62,0:19:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Setton> An anime! (lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.62,0:19:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Kanra> No, we're not, Setton.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.83,0:19:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Tanaka Tarou> It's this giant monster movie that's coming out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.13,0:19:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Saika> Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.63,0:19:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Kanra> Et tu, Tanaka Tarou?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.55,0:19:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Setton> It's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.01,0:19:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear this one had the producers changed twice, and they changed all the scriptwriters.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.55,0:19:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Saika> I'll check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.60,0:19:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Kanra> By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.06,0:19:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this is just a rumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.39,0:19:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,<Tanaka Tarou> What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.18,0:19:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard the general of the Yellow Scarves is gonna challenge the boss of the Dollars to a showdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.73,0:19:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.28,0:19:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Masaomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you going home without going to class?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.99,0:19:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You took yesterday off, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.75,0:19:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look better.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.42,0:19:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Kida...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.33,0:19:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.38,0:19:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takeguchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:20:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuugamine, did you tell someone I was in the Dollars?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.59,0:20:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, too, Kida?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.68,0:20:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.39,0:20:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you hear about how they're fighting the Yellow Scarves?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.14,0:20:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone was asking about me yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.52,0:20:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.81,0:20:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.11,0:20:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.40,0:20:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.03,0:20:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.53,0:20:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.82,0:20:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.41,0:20:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got something to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.24,0:20:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My hordes of female fans won't let me go...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.87,0:20:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let them have their fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.12,0:20:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.29,0:20:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Masaomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.38,0:20:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, no picking fights with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.46,0:20:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they provoke you, don't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But General...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.88,0:20:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give them any reason to come after us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.63,0:20:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the Slasher is part of the Dollars, get proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.22,0:20:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,General, you said you were going to ask an acquaintance about the Dollars' boss. Did you learn anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.40,0:20:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.31,0:21:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some are saying, after what happened two days ago, they can't just sit back and take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.65,0:21:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they go out of control...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be ready if that happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.77,0:21:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you why this is happening to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.56,0:21:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have a color.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.85,0:21:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You thought that meant you were safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.32,0:21:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.82,0:21:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the real world, no one will come to save you without a color.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.82,0:21:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A group with no ties to each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.29,0:21:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.79,0:21:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.75,0:22:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a bunch of kids screwing around on the internet!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.88,0:22:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll eliminate you from reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.71,0:22:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.92,0:22:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Yellow Scarves!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.76,0:22:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes, reality ends up like something out of the 2D world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.18,0:22:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Masaomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.73,0:22:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takeguchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.35,0:22:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was hit by the Yellow Scarves.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.36,0:22:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takeguchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.48,0:22:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to see him in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.95,0:23:58.45,Default-no margin,,0000,0000,0000,,This program is a work of fiction. Any resemblance to people, parties, or situations is purely coincidental.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.29,0:24:02.71,LOL ITALICS,,0000,0000,0000,,That time... why didn't I stop then?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.17,0:24:05.67,LOL ITALICS,,0000,0000,0000,,What do I know about the Dollars?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.38,0:24:09.42,LOL ITALICS,,0000,0000,0000,,If I stay like this, nothing will change.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.42,0:24:10.13,LOL ITALICS,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.88,0:24:11.88,Default-no margin,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.88,0:24:14.28,Default-no margin,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything Covered in Fog.
